  "texts": [
    "4) Comprehensive and deeper exploration of different concerns in HFM.",
    "This survey has explored comprehensive contents including the methods, data, applications, challenges, and future directions.",
    "Compared with the existing surveys [10], [56], [57], it provides a complete vision for HFM so that the readers will achieve a deeper understanding.This survey provides insight into the healthcare foundation models and our contributions are listed below:1) Systematic Review of Methods (Section II): A total of 200 technical papers from 2018 to 2024 (Jan-Feb) related to HFMs are enrolled in this survey.",
    "We presented a novel taxonomy for these papers and reviewed them in the pre-training and adaptation for language, vision, bioinformatics, and multimodal sub-fields.",
    "It provides insights into the potential technical innovations for healthcare foundation models."
  ]
